{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":691,"text":"Almost a year ago,"},{"time":2036,"text":"my aunt started suffering back pains."},{"time":4897,"text":"She went to see the doctor"},{"time":6262,"text":"and they told her it was a normal injury"},{"time":8511,"text":"for someone who had been playing tennis"},{"time":10165,"text":"for almost 30 years."},{"time":12190,"text":"They recommended that she do some therapy,"},{"time":14158,"text":"but after a while she wasn't feeling better,"},{"time":17253,"text":"so the doctors decided to do further tests."},{"time":20593,"text":"They did an x-ray"},{"time":21592,"text":"and discovered an injury in her lungs,"},{"time":23681,"text":"and at the time they thought that the injury"},{"time":25238,"text":"was a strain in the muscles and tendons"},{"time":26796,"text":"between her ribs,"},{"time":27966,"text":"but after a few weeks of treatment,"},{"time":29735,"text":"again her health wasn't getting any better."},{"time":33793,"text":"So finally, they decided to do a biopsy,"},{"time":37483,"text":"and two weeks later,"},{"time":38700,"text":"the results of the biopsy came back."},{"time":41443,"text":"It was stage 3 lung cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46212,"text":"Her lifestyle was almost free of risk."},{"time":49114,"text":"She never smoked a cigarette,"},{"time":50847,"text":"she never drank alcohol,"},{"time":52613,"text":"and she had been playing sports"},{"time":53715,"text":"for almost half her life."},{"time":55897,"text":"Perhaps, that is why it took them almost six months"},{"time":59073,"text":"to get her properly diagnosed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62197,"text":"My story might be, unfortunately,"},{"time":64300,"text":"familiar to most of you."},{"time":66539,"text":"One out of three people sitting in this audience"},{"time":69240,"text":"will be diagnosed with some type of cancer,"},{"time":72166,"text":"and one out of four"},{"time":73312,"text":"will die because of it."},{"time":76910,"text":"Not only did that cancer diagnosis"},{"time":78992,"text":"change the life of our family,"},{"time":80859,"text":"but that process of going"},{"time":82872,"text":"back and forth with new tests,"},{"time":85480,"text":"different doctors describing symptoms,"},{"time":87248,"text":"discarding diseases over and over,"},{"time":90420,"text":"was stressful and frustrating,"},{"time":92800,"text":"especially for my aunt."},{"time":94712,"text":"And that is the way cancer diagnosis has been done"},{"time":97423,"text":"since the beginning of history."},{"time":99763,"text":"We have 21st-century medical treatments and drugs"},{"time":102609,"text":"to treat cancer,"},{"time":104172,"text":"but we still have 20th-century procedures"},{"time":106714,"text":"and processes for diagnosis, if any."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110842,"text":"Today, most of us have to wait for symptoms"},{"time":113486,"text":"to indicate that something is wrong."},{"time":115953,"text":"Today, the majority of people still don't have access"},{"time":118470,"text":"to early cancer detection methods,"},{"time":120888,"text":"even though we know"},{"time":122260,"text":"that catching cancer early"},{"time":124184,"text":"is basically the closest thing we have"},{"time":125647,"text":"to a silver bullet cure against it."},{"time":129127,"text":"We know that we can change this in our lifetime,"},{"time":131608,"text":"and that is why my team and I"},{"time":133160,"text":"have decided to begin this journey,"},{"time":135354,"text":"this journey to try to make cancer detection"},{"time":137860,"text":"at the early stages"},{"time":139405,"text":"and monitoring the appropriate \nresponse at the molecular level"},{"time":142557,"text":"easier, cheaper, smarter"},{"time":146819,"text":"and more accessible than ever before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150276,"text":"The context, of course,"},{"time":151648,"text":"is that we're living at a time"},{"time":153191,"text":"where technology is disrupting our present"},{"time":154600,"text":"at exponential rates,"},{"time":156107,"text":"and the biological realm is no exception."},{"time":159117,"text":"It is said today that biotech is advancing"},{"time":161547,"text":"at least six times faster than the growth rate"},{"time":163842,"text":"of the processing power of computers."},{"time":166218,"text":"But progress in biotech"},{"time":167530,"text":"is not only being accelerated,"},{"time":169170,"text":"it is also being democratized."},{"time":171216,"text":"Just as personal computers or the Internet"},{"time":174428,"text":"or smartphones leveled the playing field"},{"time":176879,"text":"for entrepreneurship, politics or education,"},{"time":179736,"text":"recent advances have leveled it\nup for biotech progress as well,"},{"time":183156,"text":"and that is allowing"},{"time":184449,"text":"multidisciplinary teams like ours"},{"time":186564,"text":"to try to tackle and look at these problems"},{"time":189219,"text":"with new approaches."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191570,"text":"We are a team of scientists and technologists"},{"time":194193,"text":"from Chile, Panama,"},{"time":197183,"text":"Mexico, Israel and Greece,"},{"time":200570,"text":"and based on recent scientific discoveries,"},{"time":203192,"text":"we believe that we have found"},{"time":204574,"text":"a reliable and accurate way"},{"time":207375,"text":"of detecting several types of cancer"},{"time":209377,"text":"at the very early stages through a blood sample."},{"time":212275,"text":"We do it by detecting a set of very small molecules"},{"time":215223,"text":"that circulate freely in our blood"},{"time":216892,"text":"called microRNAs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219688,"text":"To explain what microRNAs are"},{"time":221999,"text":"and their important role in cancer,"},{"time":224214,"text":"I need to start with proteins,"},{"time":225607,"text":"because when cancer is present in our body,"},{"time":228160,"text":"protein modification is observed"},{"time":229591,"text":"in all cancerous cells."},{"time":231202,"text":"As you might know,"},{"time":232575,"text":"proteins are large biological molecules"},{"time":234850,"text":"that perform different functions within our body,"},{"time":237190,"text":"like catalyzing metabolic reactions"},{"time":239275,"text":"or responding to stimuli"},{"time":241121,"text":"or replicating DNA,"},{"time":242923,"text":"but before a protein is expressed or produced,"},{"time":245666,"text":"relevant parts of its genetic code"},{"time":247364,"text":"present in the DNA"},{"time":249513,"text":"are copied into the messenger RNA,"},{"time":253482,"text":"so this messenger RNA"},{"time":255392,"text":"has instructions on how to build a specific protein,"},{"time":259106,"text":"and potentially it can build hundreds of proteins,"},{"time":261706,"text":"but the one that tells them when to build them"},{"time":264303,"text":"and how many to build"},{"time":266632,"text":"are microRNAs."},{"time":269070,"text":"So microRNAs are small molecules"},{"time":270900,"text":"that regulate gene expression."},{"time":273100,"text":"Unlike DNA, which is mainly fixed,"},{"time":275315,"text":"microRNAs can vary depending on internal"},{"time":277464,"text":"and environmental conditions at any given time,"},{"time":280321,"text":"telling us which genes are actively \nexpressed at that particular moment."},{"time":283775,"text":"And that is what makes microRNAs"},{"time":285194,"text":"such a promising biomarker for cancer,"},{"time":287495,"text":"because as you know,"},{"time":289377,"text":"cancer is a disease of altered gene expression."},{"time":293190,"text":"It is the uncontrolled regulation of genes."},{"time":296744,"text":"Another important thing to consider"},{"time":298398,"text":"is that no two cancers are the same,"},{"time":300817,"text":"but at the microRNA level, there are patterns."},{"time":303865,"text":"Several scientific studies have shown"},{"time":306115,"text":"that abnormal microRNA expression levels"},{"time":309456,"text":"varies and creates a unique, specific pattern"},{"time":312571,"text":"for each type of cancer,"},{"time":314259,"text":"even at the early stages,"},{"time":315991,"text":"reflecting the progression of the disease,"},{"time":317881,"text":"and whether it's responding to medication"},{"time":319782,"text":"or in remission,"},{"time":320990,"text":"making microRNAs a perfect,"},{"time":323123,"text":"highly sensitive biomarker."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326727,"text":"However, the problem with microRNAs"},{"time":329401,"text":"is that we cannot use existing DNA-based technology"},{"time":331950,"text":"to detect them in a reliable way,"},{"time":334563,"text":"because they are very short sequences of nucleotides,"},{"time":337353,"text":"much smaller than DNA."},{"time":339535,"text":"And also, all microRNAs are\nvery similar to each other,"},{"time":342550,"text":"with just tiny differences."},{"time":344597,"text":"So imagine trying to differentiate two molecules,"},{"time":347117,"text":"extremely similar, extremely small."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350311,"text":"We believe that we have found a way to do so,"},{"time":353217,"text":"and this is the first time that we've shown it in public."},{"time":355966,"text":"Let me do a demonstration."},{"time":358467,"text":"Imagine that next time you go to your doctor"},{"time":360908,"text":"and do your next standard blood test,"},{"time":362831,"text":"a lab technician extracts a total RNA,"},{"time":365183,"text":"which is quite simple today,"},{"time":367106,"text":"and puts it in a standard \n96-well plate like this one."},{"time":369898,"text":"Each well of these plates"},{"time":371565,"text":"has specific biochemistry that we assign,"},{"time":374204,"text":"that is looking for a specific microRNA,"},{"time":376544,"text":"acting like a trap that closes"},{"time":378323,"text":"only when the microRNA is present in the sample,"},{"time":380680,"text":"and when it does, it will shine with green color."},{"time":383801,"text":"To run the reaction,"},{"time":384904,"text":"you put the plate inside a device like this one,"},{"time":388040,"text":"and then you can put your smartphone on top of it."},{"time":391930,"text":"If we can have a camera here"},{"time":394670,"text":"so you can see my screen."},{"time":397378,"text":"A smartphone is a connected computer"},{"time":399774,"text":"and it's also a camera,"},{"time":401383,"text":"good enough for our purpose."},{"time":407431,"text":"The smartphone is taking pictures,"},{"time":409411,"text":"and when the reaction is over,"},{"time":410755,"text":"it will send the pictures"},{"time":411798,"text":"to our online database for processing"},{"time":414112,"text":"and interpretation."},{"time":415730,"text":"This entire process lasts around 60 minutes,"},{"time":418455,"text":"but when the process is over,"},{"time":420300,"text":"wells that shine are matched \nwith the specific microRNAs"},{"time":423325,"text":"and analyzed in terms of how much and how fast"},{"time":425969,"text":"they shine."},{"time":427218,"text":"And then, when this entire process is over,"},{"time":431486,"text":"this is what happens."},{"time":433944,"text":"This chart is showing the specific microRNAs"},{"time":436541,"text":"present in this sample"},{"time":437976,"text":"and how they reacted over time."},{"time":440388,"text":"Then, if we take this specific pattern of microRNA"},{"time":442890,"text":"of this person's samples"},{"time":444296,"text":"and compare it with existing scientific documentation"},{"time":447272,"text":"that correlates microRNA patterns"},{"time":449220,"text":"with a specific presence of a disease,"},{"time":454501,"text":"this is how pancreatic cancer looks like."},{"time":457950,"text":"This inside is a real sample"},{"time":460607,"text":"where we just detected pancreatic cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463926,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":472086,"text":"Another important aspect of this approach"},{"time":474444,"text":"is the gathering and mining of data in the cloud,"},{"time":476783,"text":"so we can get results in real time"},{"time":478426,"text":"and analyze them with our contextual information."},{"time":481863,"text":"If we want to better understand"},{"time":483341,"text":"and decode diseases like cancer,"},{"time":485456,"text":"we need to stop treating them"},{"time":486806,"text":"as acute, isolated episodes,"},{"time":488988,"text":"and consider and measure everything"},{"time":490912,"text":"that affects our health on a permanent basis."},{"time":495220,"text":"This entire platform is a working prototype."},{"time":499506,"text":"It uses state-of-the-art molecular biology,"},{"time":502971,"text":"a low-cost, 3D-printed device,"},{"time":505717,"text":"and data science"},{"time":507679,"text":"to try to tackle one of humanity's \ntoughest challenges."},{"time":511594,"text":"Since we believe early cancer detection"},{"time":513596,"text":"should really be democratized,"},{"time":515384,"text":"this entire solution costs at least 50 times less"},{"time":517769,"text":"than current available methods,"},{"time":519770,"text":"and we know that the community can help us"},{"time":521503,"text":"accelerate this even more,"},{"time":522988,"text":"so we're making the design of the device"},{"time":524923,"text":"open-source."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527400,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":535944,"text":"Let me say very clearly"},{"time":537541,"text":"that we are at the very early stages,"},{"time":539276,"text":"but so far, we have been able"},{"time":541257,"text":"to successfully identify the microRNA pattern"},{"time":543866,"text":"of pancreatic cancer, lung cancer,"},{"time":547128,"text":"breast cancer and hepatic cancer."},{"time":550188,"text":"And currently, we're doing a clinical trial"},{"time":553370,"text":"in collaboration with the\nGerman Cancer Research Center"},{"time":556249,"text":"with 200 women for breast cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559840,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":563448,"text":"This is the single non-invasive,"},{"time":566162,"text":"accurate and affordable test"},{"time":568904,"text":"that has the potential to dramatically change"},{"time":571150,"text":"how cancer procedures and diagnostics"},{"time":572960,"text":"have been done."},{"time":574780,"text":"Since we're looking for the microRNA patterns"},{"time":576397,"text":"in your blood at any given time,"},{"time":578962,"text":"you don't need to know\nwhich cancer you're looking for."},{"time":580858,"text":"You don't need to have any symptoms."},{"time":583025,"text":"You only need one milliliter of blood"},{"time":585833,"text":"and a relatively simple array of tools."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589343,"text":"Today, cancer detection happens mainly"},{"time":592155,"text":"when symptoms appear."},{"time":594240,"text":"That is, at stage 3 or 4,"},{"time":596869,"text":"and I believe that is too late."},{"time":598793,"text":"It is too expensive for our families."},{"time":600941,"text":"It is too expensive for humanity."},{"time":603393,"text":"We cannot lose the war against cancer."},{"time":606340,"text":"It not only costs us billions of dollars,"},{"time":608230,"text":"but it also costs us the people we love."},{"time":611152,"text":"Today, my aunt, she's fighting bravely"},{"time":614650,"text":"and going through this process\nwith a very positive attitude."},{"time":617560,"text":"However, I want fights like this"},{"time":620138,"text":"to become very rare."},{"time":621761,"text":"I want to see the day"},{"time":622888,"text":"when cancer is treated easily"},{"time":624815,"text":"because it can be routinely diagnosed"},{"time":626967,"text":"at the very early stages,"},{"time":628924,"text":"and I'm certain"},{"time":630016,"text":"that in the very near future,"},{"time":632152,"text":"because of this"},{"time":633450,"text":"and other breakthroughs that we are seeing"},{"time":634690,"text":"every day in the life sciences,"},{"time":636713,"text":"the way we see cancer"},{"time":638345,"text":"will radically change."},{"time":640336,"text":"It will give us the chance of detecting it early,"},{"time":642800,"text":"understanding it better,"},{"time":644565,"text":"and finding a cure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":646801,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":648480,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}